data.description: Beautiful family home! Featuring a split floor plan with 4 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths and an in-ground swimming pool for all of those hot Alabama days and nights!  No Carpet in this home! All hardwood floors throughout and ceramic tile in kitchen and baths. There's a large eat-in kitchen with a gas range, granite counter tops and stainless appliances. The guest bath has 2 separate sinks/vanities and the master bath has a double vanity, 2 walk in closets, and a new large soaking tub! Plantation shutters in the Master, Dining and Living room! Everything inside was repainted in 2021, new gutters, new garage door motor, and a new pool pump! In the garage you will find a staircase leading to a large floored attic space making it super easy to store things and get to the stored items. Don't miss out!
